Setup			2fmri            Setup name

### Problem parameters			         

SoundSpeedNeutral  	0.05                     h0*vk0
SoundSpeedIon    	0.05                     h0*vk0
Betaz			500.0                    Gas pressure/Magnetic Pressure
Betap			500.0e9                  Gas pressure/Magnetic Pressure
Amplitude		1.0e-6                   Perturbation amplitude
Shearparam		1.5
Epsilon			1.0e-3
Alphacol		1.0e10
Noise           0.005
### Mesh parameters			         

Ny               	128		         Number of cells in y
Nz			128                       Number of cells in z

### Physical domain			         

Ymin		       -0.025		         Left  boundary
Ymax			0.025		         Right boundary
Zmin		        0.0		         Lower boundary
Zmax			0.05  		 Upper boundary   

### Boundaries

PeriodicZ		Yes		         Periodicity in Z

### Frame of reference			         
OmegaFrame     		1.0                      Omega0 in shearing box
Frame			F                        This is always F (Fixed)

### Output control parameters		         

Ntot			220		         Total number of DT
Ninterm	 		2		         Number of DTs between outputs
DT			0.1  	      	         DT size for fine grain outputs
OutputDir		outputs/2fmri_test            Output directory